question: Tī 2007 nî ê sî, tī kuí-ê goe̍h chiah-ê chi̍t gōa pái só͘ lâi ê kó͘-phiò ê kî-tiong kàu-chòe siōng koân ê sî?
2007年第二季度（四月、五月、六月）总共购买了多少股股票？
Te a-ge goa-la̍t ê chi̍t ge̍h, choân-pō͘ bē-su chāi ē siu-bé ê kò͘-kè lāi, chòe-ko chhiau-kò͘ ê ím-chè kè-siàu sī siáⁿ-chōe?
KoaJuly it-dat 2007 'til September it-dat 2007, chiah-ê-áîⁿ ê siú chòe-chió tit-tōa ê kè-chè ū siáⁿ-khoán ê piàn-tōa?
answer: From July to September 2007, the average price paid per share showed a fluctuating but overall upward trend. It began at $89.01 in July, dipped to $87.05 in August, and then rose sharply to a quarterly peak of $90.24 in September.

question: La̍k kó͘-ba̍k ê seng-lí-ji̍t ū siáⁿ-chōe phoe chòe kó͘-á, chi̍ah chi̍t pho͘ kó͘ ê pêng-kin kè-chē sī khah-kē $76 ê?
Tī 2007 nî 7 goe̍h, pau-lí-sòan ê chi̍t-pō͘-hūn ê kó͘-á chha̍p chòe ê chi̍t-pō͘-hūn bōe-sī chham-ka kong-khai soan-pò͘ ê kè-ōe? Chiong le̍k-sò͘ chòe phò͘-cent.

Nāi-kó͘ 2007 nî 5 goe̍h ê kò͘-bái chha̍p-á ê sò͘-liōng sī 10% koh-khah ke, jî-chhiáⁿ pêng-kin kà-chîⁿ bô piàn, hit goe̍h-lêng ê chha̍p-á cheng-choân kim-ê lóng-tsóng chiàⁿ-cheh ài siók-tsōe siáⁿ-chē? kiâm-tsiói kàu siāng-chāi ê kho͘.
Tī tē-sì kuì (Sibat-go̍eh, Po̍ah-go̍eh, Cha̍p-jī-go̍eh) ê sî-kan, só͘ bé ê choân-pō͘ kó͘-phiò ê sò͘-liōng kah só͘ hō͘ ê kó͘-phiò ê pêng-kin kè-siâu ū bē chhut-lâi ê koan-hē bē?
answer: Ū, tī tē-sì kuì ê sî-kan, chin chhián-chhián ū chi̍t ê î-sè ê koan-hē. Sibat-go̍eh, bé liáu 2.2 pah-bān tiâu kó͘-phiò, kè-siâu sī $88.89. Po̍ah-go̍eh, kè-siâu dü ia̍h khì kàu $82.35, lâi bé ê kó͘-phiò siâⁿ 1.7 pah-bān tiâu. Āu-lâi tī Cha̍p-jī-go̍eh, sî-liâu koh tńg lâi $85.41, só͘ bé ê kó͘-phiò tiāu tòe lâi 1.9 pah-bān tiâu, chhián-chhián phah-phái liáu î-sè ê kui-chek, tān-sī iáu-koh piáu-bîng siōng kē ê bé kau lōng koh píng se̍h siōng kē ê kè-siâu.

question: Tī tē-saⁿ kè-tō͘ (Lī-goe̍h, Po̍at-goe̍h, Chiu-goe̍h) ê cha̍p-chi̍t-ge̍h, ū kám-mih ge̍h ê kò͘-bái liōng hām kî-thaⁿ nn̄g ge̍h pí khòaⁿ-khí-lâi sī chi̍t ê giâm-kek-koan?
answer: Lī-goe̍h 2007 sī tē-saⁿ kè-tō͘ ê giâm-kek-koan. I ê kò͘-bái liōng 1,646,251 tâi, pí Po̍at-goe̍h (2,329,478) kap Chiu-goe̍h (2,086,564) ê liōng koh-khah kē, in nn̄g ê liōng sī tùi-pī kài siong-sī ê.

question: Tùi chit ê phiau-tsū ê tsuán-tsū hâng lâi kóng, âi-mih ê kî-kan tsuán-tsū ê sî, hōo lîn teh 2007 nî 4 goe̍h 1 ji̍t kàu 6 goe̍h 30 ji̍t ê sî, kóo-sū ê sî, tsuán-tsū ê sîng-pún sī siánn-tsuánn?
2007年1月購入的股票總數是幾多？
